name: Elliott's Oyster House
description: Elliott's Oyster House is a renowned seafood restaurant located on the Seattle waterfront, offering a variety of fresh oysters and other seafood dishes.

name: Seattle Art Museum
description: Seattle Art Museum (SAM) is one of the premier art institutions in the Pacific Northwest, featuring a diverse collection of artworks spanning various cultures and periods.

name: Bellevue Art Museum
description: Bellevue Art Museum (BAM) showcases contemporary art and craft in a variety of mediums, providing a platform for both established and emerging artists.

name: Matador
description: Matador is a vibrant Mexican restaurant and tequila bar located in the heart of Redmond, offering a menu inspired by traditional flavors with a modern twist.
